---
title: Balsamic Nectarine Duck Breasts with Zesty Rice and Watercress Salad
description: Rich, juicy duck meat pairs perfectly with fruit flavors. So what better way to showcase succulent nectarines than in a pan sauce drizzled over pan-seared, crispy-skinned duck breasts? The combo is as luscious as it sounds, especially with some balsamic glaze added in to create sweet and tangy overtones. With a light almond watercress salad and zesty lemon rice on the side, it turns into the epitome of a luxurious summertime meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/balsamic-nectarine-duck-breasts-0b44da1b.jpg
